Welcome to the start of Season Six. A new season, with new wrestlers and amazing unscripted combat. A season that promises everything you have come to love and more.
Dia Zerva came to US late last season. She had two season matches then went on to finish second in the Summer Vengeance tournament. Dia also captured the welterweight champion title. She is a power to be reckoned with.
Trina Michaels is your typical Cali girl: blond, tan, huge tits, and a booming body!
No contest - Dia just abuses Trina. Major submissions, finger fucking, and severe leg scissors. After Trina's brutal loss, Dia just fucks the shit out of her for losing. A bad day for Trina Michaels; a great day for US members!
